author: @TheNormExperience
content:
Love Rio - that’s actually where my Mom grew up so it was really special to get to go visit and experience it with her when I was old enough.

Do yourself a favor and drink ALL the Guarana you can - it’s the best soda there is! I’m gonna get some delivered for Mothers Day and make my Mom some fejoida and pao de queijo. Can’t wait to show her this video!
